{
  "texts": [
    "They were measured jointly as analysis performance.",
    "Theoretically, it is possible that the AI functions contribute to a more accurate and comprehensive analysis, but the task itself takes the same amount of time.",
    "This would not be a problem, as the improved analysis performance would still be an added value.",
    "In this respect, the participants' assessment can be seen as an indication that the speed of intelligence analysis can be increased.",
    "This correlation was also confirmed in the personal feedback discussions with the participants."
  ]
